It has been 17 years since the tragic death of actress and singer Aliyah in a plane crash at the Bahamas. At the time of her death, she has just completed filming the music video for Rock the boat. She was 22 years old at the time of her death. Tributes were paid to her at time of her death by numerous artist and performers, Jay Z did a remix to her song Miss You other artists who have paid tribute to her include rap artist J cole in his song No Role Modelz and Kendrick Lamar in the song Blow my High. Here are some of her hit songs:   